          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-438-45L5-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-438-45L5-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-438-45L5-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"><hi rend="italics">Written by Dean</hi> S<hi rend="small-caps">W──T</hi>, <hi rend="italics">tho' not inserted in his</hi> Miscellanies.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-438-45L5-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-438-45L5-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-438-45L5-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-438-45L5-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-438-45L5-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-438-45L5-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-1" n="1">I.<lb/><hi rend="display-initial">A</hi>LL you that wou'd</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-2" n="2">Refine your Blood,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-3" n="3">As pure as fam'd <hi rend="italics">Lewelling</hi>,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-4" n="4">By Waters clear,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-5" n="5">Come every Year,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-6" n="6">And drink at <hi rend="italics">Bally Spelling</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-7" n="7">II.<lb/>If Spots, or Itch,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-8" n="8">The Skin enrich</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-9" n="9">With Rubies past the telling;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-10" n="10">Twill clear the Skin,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-11" n="11">Before you've have been:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-12" n="12">A Month at <hi rend="italics">Bally-Spelling</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-13" n="13">III.<lb/>If Ladies Cheek</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-14" n="14">Be green as Leek,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-15" n="15">When she comes from her Dwelling:</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-16" n="16">The kindling Rose</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-17" n="17">Within it glows,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-18" n="18">When she's at <hi rend="italics">Bally-Spelling</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-19" n="19">IV.<lb/>The sooty Brown.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-20" n="20">Who comes to Town,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-21" n="21">Grows here as fair as <hi rend="italics">Helen</hi>:</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-22" n="22">Then back she goes</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-23" n="23">To kill the Beaux,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-24" n="24">By Dint of <hi rend="italics">Bally-Spelling</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-25" n="25">V.<lb/>Our Ladies are</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-26" n="26">As fresh and fair,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-27" n="27">As <hi rend="italics">Ross</hi>, or bright <hi rend="italics">Dunkelling</hi>;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-28" n="28">And <hi rend="italics">Mars</hi> might make</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-29" n="29">A fair Mistake,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-30" n="30">Were he at <hi rend="italics">Bally-Spelling</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-31" n="31">VI.<lb/>We Men submit,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-32" n="32">As they think fit,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-33" n="33">And here is no rebelling;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-34" n="34">The Reason's plain,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-35" n="35">The Ladies reign;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-36" n="36">They're Queens at <hi rend="italics">Bally-Spelling</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-37" n="37">VII.<lb/>By matchless Charms,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-38" n="38">Unconquer'd Arms,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-39" n="39">They have the Power of quelling</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-40" n="40">Such desperate Foes,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-41" n="41">As dare oppose</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-42" n="42">Their Power at <hi rend="italics">Bally-Spelling</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-43" n="43">VII.<lb/>Cold Water turns</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-44" n="44">To Fire and burns,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-45" n="45">I know, because I fell in</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-46" n="46">A Stream, that came</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-47" n="47">From one bright Dame,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-48" n="48">Who drank at <hi rend="italics">Bally-Spelling</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-49" n="49">IX.<lb/>Fine Beaux advance,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-50" n="50">Equipt for Dance,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-51" n="51">And bring their <hi rend="italics">Anne</hi> or <hi rend="italics">Nell</hi> in,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-52" n="52">With so much Grace,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-53" n="53">I'm sure no Place</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-54" n="54">Can vie with <hi rend="italics">Bally-Spelling</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-55" n="55">X.<lb/>No Politicks,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-56" n="56">No subtle Tricks,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-57" n="57">No Man his Country selling:</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-58" n="58">We eat, we drink,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-59" n="59">We never think</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-60" n="60">Of these at <hi rend="italics">Bally-Spelling</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-61" n="61">XI.<lb/>The vex'd in Mind,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-62" n="62">The puff'd with Wind,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-63" n="63">Do all come here pell mell in;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-64" n="64">And they are sure,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-65" n="65">To work a Cure</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-66" n="66">By drinking <hi rend="italics">Bally Spelling</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-67" n="67">XII.<lb/>If Dropsy fills</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-68" n="68">You to the Gills,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-69" n="69">From Chin to Toe tho' swelling;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-70" n="70">Pour in, pour out,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-71" n="71">You cannot doubt</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-72" n="72">A Cure at <hi rend="italics">Bally-Spelling</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-73" n="73">XIII.<lb/>Death throws no Darts,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-74" n="74">Through all these Parts,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-75" n="75">No Sexton's here are knelling;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-76" n="76">Come judge and try,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-77" n="77">You'll never die,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-78" n="78">But live at <hi rend="italics">Bally-Spelling</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-79" n="79">XIV.<lb/>Except you feel</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-80" n="80">Darts tip'd with Steel,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-81" n="81">Which here are e'r revelling;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-82" n="82">When from those Eyes</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-83" n="83">Sweet Ruin flies,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-84" n="84">We die at <hi rend="italics">Bally Spelling</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-85" n="85">XV.<lb/>Good Cheer, fresh Air,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-86" n="86">Much Joy, no Care,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-87" n="87">Your Ear, your Taste, your Smelling,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-88" n="88">Your Sight, your Touch</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-89" n="89">Transported much</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-90" n="90">When you're at <hi rend="italics">Bally-Spelling</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-91" n="91">XVI.<lb/>Within this Ground</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-92" n="92">We all sleep sound;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-93" n="93">No noisy Dogs a yelling;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-94" n="94">Unless you wake</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-95" n="95">For <hi rend="italics">Celia</hi>'s sake,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-96" n="96">All Night at <hi rend="italics">Bally-Spelling</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-97" n="97">XVII.<lb/>Now you all see,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-98" n="98">Both he and she;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-99" n="99">No Ladies keep their dwelling;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-100" n="100">But all partake,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-101" n="101">The Mirth we make,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-102" n="102">When we're at <hi rend="italics">Bally-Spelling</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-103" n="103">XVIII.<lb/>My Rhimes are gone,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-104" n="104">I think I've none.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-105" n="105">Unless I should bring Hell in:</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-106" n="106">But being here,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-107" n="107">To Heav'n so near,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-438-45L5-line-108" n="108">I can't at <hi rend="italics">Bally-Spelling</hi>.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
